title: 181 - Zito's Freestyle
description: Today’s episode kicks off by none other than host Tone Digs himself. The boys kick the show off on a different note, by discussing movies and shows they have on their plate alongside the football season. The boys then jump right into the Pod FOD which is a folder compiled from all things around the internet. Today’s FOD includes the latest Ben and J-Lo rumors, Zito’s NFL Coaches fight bracket, the greatest song debate and much more. Make sure to subscribe to youtube.come/thepodpmi to watch full episodes and don't forget to send your submissions for the Pod FOD to @ThePodPMI on twitter and instagram. We appreciate you rocking with us and we'll see you Wednesday, Cheers.
